<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cairo Alexandria</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/sharm-el-sheikh/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Cairo Alexandria</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        O oportunitate fantastica sa explorezi cele mai frumoase monumente din Cairo si Alexandria. Vizita la Muzeul Egiptian de Antichitati, Marea Piramida si Sfinxul inainte sa mergem catre nordul Alexandriei ca sa exploram cele mai frumoase obiective turistice. Vizita la Alexandria Pompey Pillar, Catacombele din Kom El Shokafa, Fortul Qitbay, Biblioteca Alexandria & Moscheea Abo El Abbas de afara.                                                                                             
