        A fantastic opportunity to explore Cairo and Alexandria’s best monuments. Visit Egyptian Museum of Antiquities, Great Pyramid and Sphinx before heading north to Alexandria to explore Alexandria’s best sights. Visit Alexandria Pompey Pillar , Catacombs of Kom El Shokafa, Fort Qitbay, Alexandria bibliotheca & Abo El Abbas mosque from out side.<br><br>
